005package edu.wpi.first.math;
006
007public class Pair<A, B> {
008  private final A m_first;
009  private final B m_second;
010
011  public Pair(A first, B second) {
012    m_first = first;
013    m_second = second;
014  }
015
016  public A getFirst() {
017    return m_first;
018  }
019
020  public B getSecond() {
021    return m_second;
022  }
023
024  public static <A, B> Pair<A, B> of(A a, B b) {
025    return new Pair<>(a, b);
026  }
027}
